  [1m[38;2;125;207;255mcomment Comment by @clawsweeper 2d ago[0m[38;2;192;202;245m[48;2;26;27;38m                                                                                                                        
  Codex review: keeping this open for maintainer follow-up. Current main still has a plausible Responses replay failure                                         
  for custom openai-responses providers because generic Responses payloads can be unstored while replaying server-owned                                         
  reasoning item IDs.                                                                                                                                           
                                                                                                                                                                
